{
  "body_html": "\n\n  \n    第二节 Logstash的安装\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n  <link href=\"https://www.yuque.com/attachments/yuque/0/2020/css/491128/1588213910235-976bcd3a-7a9c-473d-b800-1b1df54807d4.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<link href=\"https://www.yuque.com/attachments/yuque/0/2020/css/491128/1588213910286-64db0dd0-ac29-46fb-9241-76ef318b1b53.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n\n  \n        \n<div class=\"page\">\n    \n        <h1 class=\"book-chapter\" id=\"calibre_toc_7\">第二节 Logstash的安装</h1>\n        <div class=\"section\">\n            <h1 id=\"第一节-logstash的安装\" class=\"calibre7\">第一节 Logstash的安装</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1、安装logstash\" class=\"calibre8\">1、安装Logstash</h2>\n<h3 id=\"11、下载签名公钥\" class=\"calibre9\">1.1、下载签名公钥</h3>\n<pre class=\"calibre10\"><code class=\"pcalibre4 pcalibre3 calibre11\">rpm --import https://packages.elastic.co/GPG-KEY-elasticsearch\n</code></pre><h3 id=\"12、创建repo文件\" class=\"calibre9\">1.2、创建repo文件</h3>\n<p class=\"calibre12\">创建文件指令：</p>\n<pre class=\"calibre10\"><code class=\"pcalibre4 pcalibre3 calibre11\">cd /etc/yum.repos.d\nsudo vi logstash.repo\n</code></pre><p class=\"calibre12\">添加文件内容：</p>\n<pre class=\"calibre10\"><code class=\"pcalibre4 pcalibre3 calibre11\">[logstash-2.3]\nname=Logstash repository for 2.3.x packages\nbaseurl=https://packages.elastic.co/logstash/2.3/centos\ngpgcheck=1\ngpgkey=https://packages.elastic.co/GPG-KEY-elasticsearch\nenabled=1\n</code></pre><h3 id=\"13、使用yum进行安装\" class=\"calibre9\">1.3、使用yum进行安装</h3>\n<pre class=\"calibre10\"><code class=\"pcalibre4 pcalibre3 calibre11\">sudo yum install logstash\n</code></pre><p class=\"calibre12\"><img alt src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/491128/1588213929382-dec6fd73-26f0-4176-b704-486568823f8d.png\" class=\"calibre14\" /></p>\n<p class=\"calibre12\">备注：所有安装过程使用anbc用户登录</p>\n<h2 id=\"2、手动安装\" class=\"calibre13\">2、手动安装</h2>\n<ul class=\"calibre17\">\n<li class=\"calibre18\">下载logstash压缩包 <pre class=\"calibre10\"><code class=\"pcalibre4 pcalibre3 calibre11\">wget https://download.elastic.co/logstash/logstash/logstash-2.3.4.tar.gz\n</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"calibre17\">\n<li class=\"calibre18\"><p class=\"calibre12\">对压缩包进行解压缩</p>\n<pre class=\"calibre10\"><code class=\"pcalibre4 pcalibre3 calibre11\">tar -xzvf logstash-2.3.4.tar.gz\n</code></pre></li>\n<li class=\"calibre18\"><p class=\"calibre12\">创建配置文件</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"calibre12\">￼</p>\n<pre class=\"calibre10\"><code class=\"pcalibre4 pcalibre3 calibre11\">[root@t0-security-tdas01 logstash-2.3.4]# cd /etc\n[root@t0-security-tdas01 etc]# mkdir logstash\n</code></pre><p class=\"calibre12\">将配置文件写到<code class=\"pcalibre5 pcalibre6 calibre19\">/etc/logstash</code>文件夹中</p>\n\n        </div>\n    \n</div>\n\n        \n    \n\n\n\n",
